20:40.123 --> 20:41.447
(water bubbles)

20:41.649 --> 20:44.483
(birds chirping)

20:44.612 --> 20:46.633
Stan, ready for a jog?

20:46.681 --> 20:47.947
STAN:
Yep! Just one minute.

20:48.048 --> 20:49.359
Stan, I love that

20:49.470 --> 20:51.316
you're beasting it
on the salmon ladder,

20:51.424 --> 20:53.672
but there's no shame
in starting basic.

20:53.712 --> 20:56.546
I know. I just think this will
be very beneficial long-term.

20:56.627 --> 20:57.893
(groans)

20:58.107 --> 20:59.784
I need to live forever.

20:59.911 --> 21:02.168
That's the spirit! (flames whoosh)
